com.veraxsystems.vxipmi.coding.rmcp

Class RmcpConstants

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.veraxsystems.vxipmi.coding.rmcp.RmcpConstants

  • public final class RmcpConstants
extends java.lang.Object
    Set of constants. Byte constants are encoded as pseudo unsigned bytes. RMCPConstants doesn't use TypeConverter because fields need to be runtime constants.
    See Also:
    TypeConverter.byteToInt(byte), TypeConverter.intToByte(int)
